By: Bulleh Shah
Format: verse
Title: One Thread Only
---
One thread, one thread only!
Warp and woof, quill and shuttle,
countless cloths and colors,

  a thousand hanks and skeins --
  with ten thousand names
  ten thousand places.

But there is one thread only.
